    "title": "Yatra Capital India is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Senior)",
    "description": "Join the Yatra Capital India family as a E-commerce Executive in Visakhapatnam. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Yatra Capital India:\nYatra Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yatra Capital India!",
